chapters.title: Chapter 11: What Lies Hidden
chapters.info: Jeaine Caide, p. 205 (177)—Aes Sedai of the Black Ajah from Arad Doman. She was openly Green Ajah until she left with Liandrin. She has coppery skin and a swan-like neck, and is fond of thin, clinging dresses. This figure and taste is similar to how Leane acts, dresses, and looks, and is typical of a Domani woman.
